item.title: About Me
item.description: Hello My name is Bagas Ari Wibowo, my friends call me Bagas, now I work as an engineer and in this platform I try to write and share notes while I work as an engineer. The Beginning Every story begins with an opening, first I would like to thank the readers who have visited this page and I hope that what is written can be understood and taken advantage of.
